<div class="title">Diet Anyone?</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Axim&Exact=1">Axim</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Axim. "Diet Anyone?: An Experience with Caffeine (exp6800)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 30, 2001. erowid.org/exp/6800</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

